---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Colophon — Munad Mahinoor"
  description="How this site is built: Astro, self-hosted variable font, no tracking, and an agent workforce directing design, build, and accessibility verification."
>
  <SiteHeader slot="header" currentPath="/colophon" />

  <section class="page-intro">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Colophon</h1>
      <p class="page-intro__lede">How this site is built.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="divider-stripe divider-stripe--muted container-hr" />

  <section class="statement">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Stack</h2>
      <p>
        Built with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Astro</a>,
        shipping essentially zero client-side JavaScript &mdash; the one exception is the
        light/dark theme toggle. Type is set in a self-hosted Archivo variable font, served
        from this site rather than a third-party font host. Hosted on Cloudflare Pages.
      </p>

      <h2>Design system</h2>
      <p>
        The visual language is op-art-inspired and accessibility-first: static line-weight
        geometry, ruled dividers, and typography carry the expression, rather than imagery,
        motion, or decoration for its own sake. Every color pairing used for text is
        contrast-checked, with body text held to AAA (7:1) rather than the AA minimum.
      </p>

      <h2>How it was made</h2>
      <p>
        This site was designed and built through an agent workforce that I directed &mdash;
        Claude models handling the design system, the page-by-page build, and accessibility
        verification, with me setting direction, reviewing output, and making the calls a
        person needs to make. It's also the subject of a forthcoming essay on the
        {' '}<a href="/writing">writing</a> page.
      </p>

      <h2>Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        No analytics, no cookies, no tracking scripts of any kind. I don't know who visits
        this site or what they look at.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SiteFooter slot="footer" />
</Base>

<style>
  .page-intro {
    padding-block: var(--space-5) var(--space-3);
  }
  .page-intro__lede {
    font-size: var(--fs-subhead);
    line-height: var(--leading-heading);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .container-hr {
    max-width: var(--container);
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-block: var(--space-3);
  }

  .statement {
    padding-block: var(--space-2) var(--space-7);
  }
  .statement :global(h2) {
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
  }
  .statement :global(h2:first-child) {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .statement :global(p) {
    max-width: var(--measure);
  }
</style>
